OL,6,FA Carlisle man made racist threats to
OL,7,Fkill a man at the city's bus station,
OL,8,Fand also verbally threatened a driver.
OL,10,FBystanders, including children, were
OL,11,Fsaid to have been affected by the
OL,12,Fcriminal conduct of 47-year-old Andrew
OL,13,FJohn Jason Bell at Lonsdale Street on
OL,14,FTuesday evening.
