OL,6,FBell had approached one Thailand-born
OL,7,Fman of mixed ethnicity as he was sat
OL,8,Fwith his partner. That man, a
OL,9,Fstranger, refused to rise to the
OL,10,Fverbal racist bait of Bell who, as he
OL,11,Fwalked away, told him: "If I see you
OL,12,Fagain I will kill you."
OL,14,FThe man feared Bell would launched an
OL,15,Fattack on the couple.
