OL,6,F"He kept touching his pocket,
OL,7,Fintimating he had something in there,"
OL,8,Fhe had told police. "I was extremely
OL,9,Fdistressed by this. I do not know this
OL,10,Fman. I do not know what he is capable
OL,11,Fof doing."
OL,13,FCarlisle Magistrates' Court heard Bell
OL,14,Fhad moved on to verbally abuse a bus
OL,15,Fdriver who was waiting to board a
OL,16,Fvehicle, causing him to fear violence
OL,17,Fwould be used. "Your days are
OL,18,Fnumbered. You are on my list," Bell
OL,19,Fhad told him.
