OL,6,FIn court on Thursday, Bell admitted
OL,7,Ftwo public order offences ` one being
OL,8,Fracially aggravated` and also causing
OL,9,Fcriminal damage to a police cell
OL,10,Fhaving urinated on a wall. A district
OL,11,Fjudge heard he had 135 previous
OL,12,Fconvictions on his record for 216 past
OL,13,Foffences.
OL,15,FDefence lawyer Kate Hunter said Bell
OL,16,Fhad intentionally used words to cause
OL,17,Fdistress but added: "His intention was
OL,18,Fnot to hurt anyone."
