OL,6,FBell was handed an immediate 20-week
OL,7,Fjail term, and must pay #100
OL,8,Fcompensation to each of his two
OL,9,Fvictims, along with #100 to the police
OL,10,Ffor damage caused.
OL,12,F"You have an appalling record. A vast
OL,13,Fnumber of your offences, certainly in
OL,14,Frecent years, have been exactly the
OL,15,Fsame as this," district judge John
OL,16,FTemperley told Bell. "There is no
OL,17,Fplace at all for that kind of
OL,18,Flanguage."
